        <Parent_String>potassium compounds [300212820], potassium and potassium compounds [300212818], inorganic material [300010360], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
